#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:27
msgid "1、QVAE 原理概括"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:29
msgid ""
"QVAE（Quantum Variational Autoencoder）是一种将 **量子生成模型** 引入 **变分自编码器 (VAE)** "
"潜空间的生成模型。其核心思想是："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:31
msgid "**用量子玻尔兹曼机（QBM）替代传统 VAE 中的先验分布，从而构建一个具有量子生成能力的潜变量模型。**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:33
msgid "模型结构"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:35
msgid "QVAE 包括以下关键组件："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:37
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**编码器（Encoder）**   将输入数据 $\\mathbf{x}$ 映射为潜变量的近似后验分布   "
"$q_\\phi(\\mathbf{z}|\\mathbf{x})$，通常由神经网络参数化。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:41
#, python-brace-format
msgid "**先验分布（Prior）**   使用 **量子玻尔兹曼机 (QBM)** 建模潜变量 $\\mathbf{z}$ 的先验分布。哈密顿量为："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:44
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"   \\mathcal{H}_\\theta = \\sum_l \\Gamma_l \\sigma_l^x + \\sum_l h_l "
"\\sigma_l^z + \\sum_{l<m} W_{lm} \\sigma_l^z \\sigma_m^z\n"
"\n"
"   "
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:49
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**解码器（Decoder）**   将潜变量 $\\mathbf{z}$ （或其连续松弛变量 $\\boldsymbol{\\zeta}$ "
"）映射回数据空间，并使用解码器重建原始数据："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:52
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"   p_\\theta(\\mathbf{x} | \\boldsymbol{\\zeta}) \\sim "
"\\text{Bernoulli}(f_\\theta(\\boldsymbol{\\zeta}))\n"
"\n"
"   "
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:57
msgid "训练目标：Q-ELBO"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:59
msgid "QVAE 使用一个 **量子下界 (Q-ELBO)** 来近似最大化对数似然："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:61
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\mathcal{L}_{\\text{Q-ELBO}} = "
"\\mathbb{E}_{q_\\phi(\\mathbf{z}|\\mathbf{x})} [\\log "
"p_\\theta(\\mathbf{x} | \\boldsymbol{\\zeta})] - "
"\\tilde{H}(q_\\phi(\\mathbf{z}|\\mathbf{x}) \\| p_\\theta(\\mathbf{z}))\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:66
msgid "QBM 采样与训练"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:68
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**正相（positive phase）**：从编码器采样 $\\mathbf{z} \\sim "
"q_\\phi(\\mathbf{z}|\\mathbf{x})$"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:69
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**负相（negative phase）**：从 QBM 中采样 $\\mathbf{z} \\sim "
"p_\\theta(\\mathbf{z})$，使用 **蒙特卡洛方法** 或 **量子退火器**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:71
msgid "把能量作为目标函数，objective 的梯度即为基于正相和负相采样计算的梯度。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:74
msgid "2. 模型架构"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:76
msgid "定义了用于自编码器架构的 `Encoder` 和 `Decoder` 两个模块，均继承自 `nn.Module`。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/qvae_mnist.md:78
msgid ""
"两者结构对称：包含一个全连接层、层归一化（LayerNorm）和双曲正切激活函数，并支持通过 L2 权重衰减进行正则化。 "
"编码器将高维输入映射到低维潜在空间，而解码器尝试从潜在表示重构原始输入。 每个模块提供 `get_weight_decay` "
"方法，用于在训练损失中显式加入权重正则项，以提升模型泛化能力并防止过拟合。"
msgstr ""

